SHALL NOT AFFILIATE WITH, OWN, CONTROL, VOLUNTEER OR BE EMPLOYED BY A BUSINESS OR ORGANIZATION THAT CAUSES HIM TO REGULARLY CONTACT PERSONS UNDER THE AGE OF 18; SHALL NOT AFFILIATE WITH, OWN, CONTROL, VOLUNTEER OR BE EMPLOYED IN ANY CAPACITY BY A BUSINESS WHOSE PRINCIPAL PRODUCT IS PRODUCTION OR SELLING OF MATERIALS DEPICTING OR DESCRIBING ?SEXUALLY EXPLICIT CONDUCT?;
